Invocation Name: hit radio seventies
des: Tune into Hit Radio 70s, with Dean Miuccio. It's your dedicated channel for the timeless classics that defined the vibrant and revolutionary sounds of the 1970s. With a carefully curated playlist, we preserve the spirit and energy of this iconic era, offering a sonic journey through the best hits of rock, disco, funk, and soul. Whether you're revisiting the decade or discovering it for the first time, Hit Radio 70s brings the unforgettable music of the 70s to life.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
